                     <interp inst="t17800510-11-off62" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17800510-11-off62" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing a piece of worked muslin, containing ten yards, value 4 l. 10 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17800510-11-victim166" type="victimName">
