                  , privily and secretly in the shop of the said Thomas
            </rs>, <rs id="t17800510-11-cd63" type="crimeDate">May 2d.</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17800510-11-off62 t17800510-11-cd63"></join>
